# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# dotori-ver2 — 환경변수 템플릿
# Copy to .env.local and fill in real values
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── Auth ──
NEXTAUTH_URL=http://localhost:3000
NEXTAUTH_SECRET=your_random_secret_at_least_32_chars
AUTH_SECRET=your_random_secret_at_least_32_chars
GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_xxxxxxxxxxxx

# ── AI ──
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-xxxxxxxxxxxx
AI_PROVIDER=anthropic
AI_MODEL=claude-opus-4-6

# ── AI Fallback (Phase 2) ──
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-xxxxxxxxxxxx
OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini
OPENAI_TEMPERATURE=0.55
OPENAI_TOP_P=0.95
OPENAI_MAX_TOKENS=1200

# ── Spark (Phase 2) ──
SPARK_API_KEY=your_spark_api_key
SPARK_API_URL=https://api.spark.local/v1
SPARK_MODEL=spark-5.3
SPARK_TEMPERATURE=0.35
SPARK_MAX_TOKENS=1800
SPARK_REASONING=true

# ── Kakao ──
KAKAO_CLIENT_ID=your_kakao_rest_api_key
KAKAO_CLIENT_SECRET=your_kakao_client_secret
AUTH_KAKAO_ID=your_kakao_rest_api_key
AUTH_KAKAO_SECRET=your_kakao_client_secret
NEXT_PUBLIC_KAKAO_KEY=your_kakao_javascript_key
NEXT_PUBLIC_KAKAO_MAP_KEY=your_kakao_map_app_key
KAKAO_REST_API_KEY=your_kakao_rest_api_key

# ── Naver ──
NAVER_CLIENT_ID=your_naver_client_id
NAVER_CLIENT_SECRET=your_naver_client_secret

# ── Database ──
MONGODB_URI=mongodb+srv://user:password@cluster/dotori?retryWrites=true&w=majority
MONGODB_DB_NAME=dotori
DATABASE_URL=mongodb://localhost:27018/dotori?replicaSet=rs0
SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_supabase_anon_key
SUPABASE_SERVICE_KEY=your_supabase_service_key
SUPABASE_DATABASE_URL=postgresql://postgres:password@db.your-project.supabase.co:5432/postgres

# ── Cache ──
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379

# ── Maps ──
NEXT_PUBLIC_MAPBOX_TOKEN=pk.your_mapbox_token
NEXT_PUBLIC_MAPBOX_STYLE=mapbox://styles/mapbox/light-v11

# ── Public Data ──
PUBLIC_DATA_API_KEY=your_data_go_kr_key
DATA_GO_KR_KEY=your_data_go_kr_key
YOUTUBE_API_KEY=your_youtube_api_key

# ── Payment ──
TOSS_SECRET_KEY=test_sk_xxxxxxxx
NEXT_PUBLIC_TOSS_CLIENT_KEY=test_ck_xxxxxxxx

# ── Monitoring ──
NEXT_PUBLIC_SENTRY_DSN=https://xxx@sentry.io/xxx
SENTRY_AUTH_TOKEN=your_sentry_auth_token
CODECOV_TOKEN=your_codecov_token

# ── Deploy ──
VERCEL_TOKEN=your_vercel_token
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=http://localhost:3000
NODE_ENV=development

# ── Cron ──
CRON_SECRET=your_cron_secret
